Package: reaver
Version: 1.6.6
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: root-repo
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, make, libpcap, libnl
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/t6x/reaver-wps-fork-t6x
Description: Brute force WPS PINs and recover WPA/WPA2 passphrases
 Reaver implements a brute force attack against WPS (Wi-Fi Protected Setup)
 PINs to recover the WPA/WPA2 passphrase. This is the t6x fork with
 improvements and bug fixes.
